      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a solid, functional option for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. The engine and transmission are in working order, though you should expect some minor fluid seeps and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has its share of character marks, including some paint fading on the hood and minor door dings. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get fully cold. It is a dependable car that gets the job done, perfect for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
