      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Available now is a truly exceptional vehicle in absolute mint, showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained and looks as though it just rolled off the assembly line, featuring flawless paint and a pristine interior that still feels brand new. Mechanically, it is in perfect working order with a smooth engine and transmission, reflecting its history of careful ownership. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber that requires no additional work or repairs.",
