    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an uncompromising example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in true showroom condition, reflecting a level of care and preservation rarely seen on the market. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail has been meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards of the discerning collector. Offering a seamless driving experience and a complete service history, this is an investment-grade opportunity for those who demand nothing less than perfection. Experience the pinnacle of pre-owned quality today.",
      "price": 48900.0,
